        <updateDate>2016-02-17T18:01:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill amends the Help America Vote Act of 2002 to require each state to: (1) allow individuals to vote in a federal election before the date of the election through early voting or voting by mail, and (2) publicize the details of such voting.</p>]]></text>
